    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 已购玩家可以免费获得iOS端版本的工业战争授权，领取步骤如下：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. 在游戏主界面打开【兑换】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. 输入有效邮箱及密码</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. 到Appstore 搜索 工业战争下载；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. 在iOS设备上登录 第2步所注册的邮箱和密码，即可激活开玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2025年7月更新内容：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. 新增了民国时期的上海、天津、武汉、广州、南京、重庆、沈阳、泉州、大连等都市；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. 完整更新了产品生产界面，无需反复跳转查看数据；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. 优化程序执行机制，加快运行速度；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/45f80dd4220c02fd5641b8d0f57e38e2.avif?t=1754323331\" width=1080 height=596 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/fa4f07f7a20a4ceabaedfb079278792d.avif?t=1754323331\" width=1080 height=754 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/7451eedec1be8da30d7b766c4adb4830.avif?t=1754323331\" width=1080 height=608 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2024年6月更新内容：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>新增了30多种作战兵种</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们新增了五款特殊陆战武器，有“破阵重炮”的履带火炮，有“排山倒海”的自行速射炮，有“深入敌阵，与敌同归于尽”的爆破装甲车，有“近身搏斗”的火焰喷射车，还有“穿插敌后”的突击坦克。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/b438bebc71d78795a2ccf69818e20333.poster.avif?t=1754323331\" width=480 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/b438bebc71d78795a2ccf69818e20333.webm?t=1754323331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/b438bebc71d78795a2ccf69818e20333.mp4?t=1754323331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/aca35550c9c29b05becdcc4704483aee.poster.avif?t=1754323331\" width=480 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/aca35550c9c29b05becdcc4704483aee.webm?t=1754323331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/aca35550c9c29b05becdcc4704483aee.mp4?t=1754323331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/93292c2b5dae2deb42af51b71753cc38.poster.avif?t=1754323331\" width=480 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/93292c2b5dae2deb42af51b71753cc38.webm?t=1754323331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/93292c2b5dae2deb42af51b71753cc38.mp4?t=1754323331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/e4eca08c95aa5902d7ca551f611aaa45.poster.avif?t=1754323331\" width=480 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/e4eca08c95aa5902d7ca551f611aaa45.webm?t=1754323331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/e4eca08c95aa5902d7ca551f611aaa45.mp4?t=1754323331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/97f8da880a9ca5f61e0a315bf32bee20.poster.avif?t=1754323331\" width=480 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/97f8da880a9ca5f61e0a315bf32bee20.webm?t=1754323331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/97f8da880a9ca5f61e0a315bf32bee20.mp4?t=1754323331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2024年5月更新内容：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更新北洋军阀时期、大革命时期的剧本：<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/a8926cf23c1dd7f6c285423c37be5878.avif?t=1754323331\" width=1600 height=894 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/02986ac0da98d6cf420f5fb365bf2dbc.avif?t=1754323331\" width=1600 height=994 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340600/extras/14dacd7a26a925246c454069cfe8c64b.avif?t=1754323331\" width=1368 height=1058 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20世纪初，西方世界进入了“大工业”时代，科技在化工、军工、食品、机械等领域都有很大发展。《工业战争》围绕着资源、科技、资本、市场和运输线五大要素，呈现各国的自身建设、殖民掠夺、资本渗透和正面冲突！应用里真实描绘了世界各大城市及周边工矿、农村的经济循环，您可以对自己国家的每一个城市、港口、矿场、军事要塞进行精心布局建设。在电力、资源和生产中充分配合，建设一个屹立不倒的国家，一个强大的经济实体。</p>",
